quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  56,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  56,1,jab waqay honay wali waqay hojaye
  56,2,is ke waqay honay mein kuch jhoot nahi
  56,3,kisi ko pust kere kisi ko buland
  56,4,jab zameen bhonchal se larazne lagey
  56,5,aur pahar toot kar rezah rezah ho jaien
  56,6,phir gubhar ho kar urnay lagen
  56,7,aur tum log teen qisam hojao
  56,8,to dahinay haath walay ( subhan allah ) dahinay haath walaykiya ( hi chain mein ) hain
  56,9,aur baen haath walay ( afsos ) baen haath walaykiya ( girftar azaab ) hain
  56,10,aur jo agay bherne walay hain ( un kakiya kehna ) woh agay hi bherne walay hain
  56,11,wohi ( khuda ke ) Maqarrab hain
  56,12,Nemat ke bahishtoon mein
  56,13,woh bohat se to aglay logon mein se hon ge
  56,14,aur thoray se pichlon mein se
  56,15,( Laal o Yaqoot waghera se ) jurey hue takhton par
  56,16,aamnay samnay takiya lagaye hue
  56,17,nojawan khidmat guzaar jo hamesha ( aik hi haalat mein ) rahen ge un ke aas paas phrin ge
  56,18,yani aab -khoray aur aaftabay aur saaf sharaab ke glass le le kar
  56,19,is se nah to sir mein dard hoga aur nah un ki aqlain zael hon gi
  56,20,aur meway jis terhan ke un ko pasand hon
  56,21,aur parindon ka gosht jis qisam ka un ka jee chahay
  56,22,aur barri barri aankhon wali hooren
  56,23,jaisay ( hifazat se ) teh kiye hue ( aabb daar ) moti
  56,24,yeh un aamaal ka badla hai jo woh karte they
  56,25,wahan nah behooda baat sunen ge aur nah gaali galoch
  56,26,haan un ka kalaam salam salam ( hoga )
  56,27,aur dahinay haath walay ( subhan allah ) dahinay haath walaykiya ( hi aish mein ) hain
  56,28,( yani ) be khaar ki bairyon
  56,29,aur teh bah teh kilon
  56,30,aur lambay lambay saayon
  56,31,aur pani ke jharnon
  56,32,aur mewa ha-ay kaseerah ( ke baghoon ) mein
  56,33,jo nah kabhi khatam hon aur nah un se koi rokay
  56,34,aur ounchay ounchay farshon mein
  56,35,hum ne un ( hurron ) ko pedakiya
  56,36,to un ko kanwariyan banaya
  56,37,( aur shoharon ki ) piyariyan aur hum Umar
  56,38,yani dahinay haath walon ke liye
  56,39,( yeh ) bohat se aglay logon mein se hain
  56,40,aur bohat se pichlon mein se
  56,41,aur baen haath walay ( afsos ) baen haath walaykiya ( hi azaab mein ) hain
  56,42,( yani dozakh ki ) lapat aur kholtey hue pani mein
  56,43,aur siyah dhowen ke saaye mein
  56,44,( jo ) nah thanda ( hai ) nah khushnuma
  56,45,yeh log is se pehlay Aish Naeem mein parre hue they
  56,46,aur gunah azeem par uray hue they
  56,47,aur kaha karte they ke bhala jab hum margaye aur matti hogaye aur haddiyan ( hi haddiyan reh gay ) tokiya hamein phir uthna hoga ?
  56,48,aurkiya hamaray baap dada ko bhi ?
  56,49,keh do ke be shak pehlay aur pichlle
  56,50,( sab ) aik roz muqarrar ke waqt par jama kiye jayen ge
  56,51,phir tum ae jhutlanay walay gumrah ho !
  56,52,thohar (zaqqoom) ke darakht khao ge
  56,53,aur isi se pait bharo ge
  56,54,aur is par kholta howa pani piyo ge
  56,55,aur piyo ge bhi to is terhan jaisay pyase oont peetay hain
  56,56,jaza ke din yeh un ki ziyafat hogi
  56,57,hum ne tum ko ( pehli baar bhi to ) pedakiya hai to tum ( dobarah utney ko ) kyun sach nahi samajte ?
  56,58,dekho to ke jis ( nutfay ) ko tum ( aurton ke reham mein ) daaltay ho
  56,59,kiya tum is ( se ensaan ) ko banatay ho ya hum banatay hain ?
  56,60,hum ne tum mein marna thehra diya hai aur hum is ( baat ) se aajiz nahi
  56,61,ke tumhari terhan ke aur log tumhari jagah le ayen aur tum ko aisay Jahan mein jis ko tum nahi jantay peda kar den
  56,62,aur tum ne pehli paidaiesh to jaan hi li hai. phir tum sochte kyun nahi ?
  56,63,bhala dekho to ke jo kuch tum botay ho
  56,64,tokiya tum usay ogatay ho ya hum ogatay hain ?
  56,65,agar hum chahain to usay choora choora kar dein aur tum baatein banatay reh jao
  56,66,( ke haae ) hum to muft tawwan mein phas gay
  56,67,balkay hum hain hi be naseeb
  56,68,bhala dekho to ke jo pani tum peetay ho
  56,69,kiya tum ne is ko baadal se nazilkiya hai ya hum nazil karte hain ?
  56,70,agar hum chahain to hum usay khaari kar dein phir tum shukar kyun nahi karte ?
  56,71,bhala dekho to jo aag tum darakht se nikaltay ho
  56,72,kiya tum ne is ke darakht ko pedakiya hai ya hum peda karte hain ?
  56,73,hum ne usay yaad dilanay aur musafiron ke baratnay ko banaya hai
  56,74,to tum apne perwar-digaar buzurag ke naam ki tasbeeh karo
  56,75,hamein taron ki manzlon ki qasam
  56,76,aur agar tum samjhoo to yeh barri qisam hai
  56,77,ke yeh barray rutbey ka quran hai
  56,78,( jo ) kitaab mehfooz mein ( likha howa hai )
  56,79,is ko wohi haath lagatay hain jo pak hain
  56,80,perwar-digaar aalam ki taraf se utaara gaya hai
  56,81,kiya tum is kalaam se inkaar karte ho ?
  56,82,aur apna wazifa yeh banatay ho ke ( usay ) jutlatay ho
  56,83,bhala jab rooh gilaay mein aa pahunchti hai
  56,84,aur tum is waqt ki ( haalat ko ) dekha karte ho
  56,85,aur hum is ( marnay walay ) se tum se bhi ziyada nazdeek hotay hain lekin tum ko nazar nahi atay
  56,86,pas agar tum kisi ke bas mein nahi ho
  56,87,to agar sachey ho to rooh ko phair kyun nahi letay ?
  56,88,phir agar woh ( khuda ke ) muqarabon mein se hai
  56,89,to ( is ke liye ) aaraam aur khushbodar phool aur Nemat ke baagh hain
  56,90,aur agar woh dayen haath walon mein se hai
  56,91,to ( kaha jaye ga ke ) tujh par dahinay haath walon ki taraf se salam
  56,92,aur agar woh jhutlanay walay gumrahon mein se hai
  56,93,to ( is ke liye ) kholtey pani ki ziyafat hai
  56,94,aur jahannum mein daakhilkiya jana
  56,95,yeh ( daakhilkiya jana yaqeenan sahih yani ) haq al-yaqeen hai
  56,96,to tum apne perwar-digaar buzurag ke naam ki tasbeeh karte raho
